OpenGovernment,is,a,non,partisan,project,of,the,Participatory,Politics,Foundation,and,the,Sunlight,Foundation,OpenGovernment,is,modeled,after,OpenCongress,another,project,of,this,team,but,brings,government,transparency,down,to,state,and,local,levels,The,aim,of,OpenGovernment,is,to,make,this,government,data,and,information,more,easily,accessible,and,usable,OpenGovernment,provides,a,RESTful,API,which,returns,responses,in,JSON,and,JSONP,Data,is,available,for,basics,of,legislature,and,sessions,people,committees,and,committee,memberships,bills,votes,and,more